snippet.title: Bubsy II Trailer 1994
snippet.description:
Bubsy II Trailer 1994

Official Content From Accolade

Reach Oinker P. Hamm and defeat him. In order to get to the big pig, you must travel all the levels of the Amazatorium. Don't get lost and you'll bring home the bacon!
Platforms: Sega Genesis

Sega Genesis
